'''Bryce''' is one of the men who played basketball against Sam, Pete, and Cooper.

==History==
Bryce was playing basketball against Sam, Pete, and Cooper while Naomi watched. She thought he was cute, so she asked Sam to call him and give Bryce her number. Sam agreed to call, but didn't because he was jealous. Sam finally did make the call and Bryce and Naomi set up a dinner date.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
He and [[Naomi Bennett]] had a mutual attraction.
